{"tid":1442470,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣］全力針對黑警，對未來需要打官司既義士有幫助","createTime":"2019-08-11T03:24:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T03:46:38.000Z","uid":16367,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2c46fce1a9a54e55a2d2a0a9edb7a4d755de50ba","tid":1442470,"uid":16367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:24:13.000Z","msg":"岩岩出面有大量Post已經講左要煲大721。<br />\n<br />\n仲有少少野要補充，如果將來有義士要打官司，<span style=\"color: red;\">我唔敢講100%幫到，但或多或少都有機會幫到佢地。</span><br />\n<br />\n因為專業人士/無犯過勞資法例既商人/<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警</span></span>，會被預設係誠實可靠既人。<br />\n<br />\n一般專業人士，獲取資業資格（考牌），會有行業對個人既操守/道德標準和規範。所以上到法庭，係會加分。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無犯過勞資法例既商人，作為一個老闆次次準時出糧，有多無少，幫你供MPF，比足勞工假有薪假你。你可能覺得應份。但亦都可以塑造成為一個殷實商人既形象。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑警既形象就係受過專業訓練，有入職前有品格審查，有紀律，有基本法律知識。所以黑警係法庭都係會被預設係誠實可靠證人。（但實際根本唔撚係咁呀嗎）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以，我要全力攻擊擊黑警既形象，令佢地既供詞係法庭上唔會被預先考慮為誠實可靠既人！！！依個方向係正確</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我唔敢講一定對義士有幫助，但起碼有理由值得嘗試<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自推十次。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1afea0be59ed76b38e1abf966499e90b634c85b4","tid":1442470,"uid":16367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:25:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669428208e96bdd5ba97a9ec2fd48dcd3c10d7b9","tid":1442470,"uid":16367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ea69e42a15c1bae756cdbe3f05f173c006ea43","tid":1442470,"uid":16367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d24cc01a85f243a8d40690e535a758df823c0faf","tid":1442470,"uid":16367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:28:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"862513e94ce457579561a998b627ea7b69c13248","tid":1442470,"uid":16367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:28:12.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"f301e34da17f4ad099a131ed6982de16a37791a1","tid":1442470,"uid":16367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:29:27.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"e2853ec5a98318ddb7e885385a01d344555a4b31","tid":1442470,"uid":16367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:31:50.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"9fd09ecd6aac3160c39c97d1aeae291cb794f4da","tid":1442470,"uid":16367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:33:04.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"57274388f27a358333d4c3395ab71a156cf1bbd6","tid":1442470,"uid":16367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:37:20.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"9550d1b639f113fcfdd8787df7c3940dd37d959f","tid":1442470,"uid":16367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:41:58.000Z","msg":"原來有個巴打已經開左Post講。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n此Post已完"},{"pid":"157d121a46034425def2b4cebcd0ee680528edae","tid":1442470,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:46:38.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"}]}